org.jemmy.control

Annotation Type MethodProperties


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
@Inherited
@Documented
public @interface MethodProperties
    This lists names of wrapped object's methods which could be accessed through Wrap.getProperty(String) interface. Methods should be public and should not have any parameters.
    Author:
    shura
    See Also:
    Wrap.getProperty(java.lang.String)

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String[] value
      List of method names

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.Class[] types
      List of field types.
      boolean[] waitable
      Are the properties worth a waiter.

    • Element Detail

      • value

        public abstract java.lang.String[] value
        List of method names

      • types

        public abstract java.lang.Class[] types
        List of field types. In case this list is shorter, all the unmatched ones from value are considered to be of type Object.
        Default:
        {}

      • waitable

        public abstract boolean[] waitable
        Are the properties worth a waiter.
        Default:
        {}
